      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. everything is just... dying. the oceans, the forests, the weather... it feels like we're just watching a slow motion car crash that we can't stop. what is even the point of trying to build a life or a future when the foundation is literally crumbling? it feels so stupid to keep going like nothing is wrong.",
